  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To determine the efficacy and toxicity of the combination of mitoxantrone hydrochloride (
      Novantrone ) and etoposide in the treatment of patients with HIV associated lymphomas.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
